svg.title: getIntersectionList() on element with intersecting bounding box
svg.script: test(t => { const svg = document.documentElement; const queryRect = document.getElementById('e1').getBBox(); const list = svg.getIntersectionList(queryRect, null); const result = Array.from(list).map(e => e.id).sort(); assert_array_equals(result, ['e0', 'e1']); });
